cat << EOF
A portable version of the OpenBSD `doas` command. doas is a minimal
replacement for the venerable sudo. The doas program has a simpler
configuration file and is quite small, keeping the code tiny and, one
hopes, secure. The doas command first appeared in OpenBSD 5.8.
EOF
